        {
            "block_label": "figure_title",
            "block_content": "<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Figure 9. TinyChat provides a turn-key solution to transform the theoretical memory footprint reduction into a quantifiable speedup. As a result, TinyChat is up to  $ 3.9\\times $ and  $ 3.5\\times $ faster than the FP16 implementation from Huggingface on 4090 (desktop GPU) and Orin (mobile GPU), respectively. AWQ also democratizes Llama-2-13B deployment on laptop GPUs (4070) with merely 8GB memory.</div>\n",
